  <official_title>Comparison of the Efficacy of Compliant Oral Iron Treatment (FerroDuretter ®) for 3 Months After Discharge Versus Single-dose of Intravenous Iron (Ferinject ®) Before Discharge in Patients With Acute Bleeding From Upper Gastrointestinal Tract. A Double Blinded Randomized Trial</official_title>
